										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p style="font-size: 18px"><img decoding="async" src="https://www.atfx.com.bz/hubfs/ATFX_10_most_influential_brand_2021.jpg" alt="ATFX_10_most_influential_brand_2021" width="2000" loading="lazy" style="width: 2000px"></p>
